{"tid":1549900,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"又有師傅話見到太子站有義士靈魂徘徊","createTime":"2019-09-07T13:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T14:15:16.000Z","uid":20134,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b92d3860f44a8d4d1e1f80be73f79d0c5733891c","tid":1549900,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:15:58.000Z","msg":"//有很多朋友pm我話有人見到義士的靈，問我可不可以幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n我今早一點左右去了太子，的確有一位義士靈魂係到。<br />\n<br />\n後生仔十八至二十，戴黑色眼鏡，體形較瘦。<br />\n<br />\n身穿黃色頭盔，黑衫，藍褲，黑色背包一個<br />\n<br />\n由於過程有好大外力干擾，我只能得到以下資訊<br />\n<br />\n姓陳，天水圍區，大機會在天澤村！<br />\n<br />\n不過我不太肯定。<br />\n<br />\n傳聞另外兩位見不到，或許下次再去睇下。<br />\n<br />\n後補有道士作法干擾，佢哋可能是警隊入邊的法科，目的不被可見到的人接觸！真係好仆街！<br />\n<br />\n#831黑警屠城<br />\n#freedomhk//<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5a4c9132333be5003506626bb081f4e350219b","tid":1549900,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PNroDGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPNroDGY.jpg&h=5948be32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPv47Aj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPv47Aj.png&h=e5f1a579&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9YcZWtE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9YcZWtE.jpg&h=8c06ca8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQEhH8E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQEhH8E.jpg&h=50e3b7e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd6232687b05273190fa7df3c95db2601ddf937b","tid":1549900,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:17:30.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"50ba1564da50d09de1656930f52b5bdf884424ef","tid":1549900,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:18:31.000Z",